window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A new Prism has appeared, but the monster waves are coming faster than ever.</p> <p>Will humanity's hope prove to be too little, too late?</p> <p>Meanwhile, Aden has too many voices to listen to. This is his life, but it turns out much of what he thought he knew about his past may be false.</p> <p>Is it really destiny if it has been tinkered with?</p> <p>He will have to find his place while building his team, training, and facing off against new threats.</p> <p>Perhaps the worst monsters are those wearing human skin.</p>"; 
